  "profileFieldsSaveFailed": "Account created, but ရွေးချယ်ချက် ပရိုဖိုင် fields (ရက်စွဲ of birth, gender, blood type) couldn't be saved. You can တည်းဖြတ် them later in ပရိုဖိုင် > တည်းဖြတ် Pပရိုဖိုင်",
  "privacyPolicyTitle": "ကိုယ်ရေးအချက်အလက် Policy",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Last updated: March 2025",
  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your ကိုယ်ရေးအချက်အလက် is paramount. This ကိုယ်ရေးအချက်အလက် Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "1. Data Collection",
  "privacyDataCollectionBody": "We collect the following categories of data: • Personal Information: Nအမည် အီးမေးလ် address, ဖုန်း number, ရက်စွဲ of birth, and gender. • ကျန်းမာရေး Data: Blood type, aဓာတ်မတည့်မှု chronic conditions, mဆေးဝါးများ vital signs, symptom logs, and Triage results. • အရေးပေါ် Contacts: Names, ဖုန်း numbers, and relationships of your designated contacts. • Device Data: Device type, operating system, and app version for compatibility and sပံ့ပိုးမှု • Usage Data: Feature interactions and anonymized analytics to improve our services. We only collect data that is necessary for providing our ကျန်းမာရေး companion services. You have full control over what information you provide.",
  "privacySectionDataStorage": "2. Data Storage & Encryption",
  "privacyDataStorageBody": "Your data is stored using industry-leading security measures:\n\n• Encryption at Rest: All data stored in our databases is encrypted using AES-256 encryption.\n• Encryption in Transit: All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses TLS 1.3 encryption.\n• Health Passport: Your health passport data is encrypted with a unique key derived from your credentials.\n• QR ကုဒ် Sharing: Shared health data via QR codes is encrypted and time-limited.\n• Infrastructure: Our servers are hosted in SOC 2 Type II certified data centers with 24/7 monitoring.\n\nWe do not store payment card information. All payment processing is handled by certified third-party providers.",
  "privacySectionGdpr": "3. GDPR Compliance",
  "privacyGdprBody": "{appName} is fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR): • Lawful Basis: We process your data based on your explicit consent and contractual necessity. • Data Minimization: We only collect and process data that is strictly necessary. • Purpose Limitation: Your data is used only for the purposes for which it was collected. • Right to Access: You can request a complete copy of your personal data at any tအချိန် • Right to Rectification: You can update or correct your data through the app sဆက်တင်များ • Right to Erasure: You can request complete deletion of your account and data. • Right to Portability: You can တင်ပို့ your data in a machine-readable format. • Data Processing Agreements: အားလုံး third-party processors have signed DPAs. • Cross-Border Transfers: Data is processed within the EU/EEA unless explicit consent is given otherwise.",
  "privacySectionYourRights": "4. Your Rights",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your data: • Access: View အားလုံး your personal and ကျန်းမာရေး data within the app or request a data eတင်ပို့ • Correction: တည်းဖြတ် your ပရိုဖိုင် information at any အချိန် through တည်းဖြတ် Pပရိုဖိုင် • Deletion: Request account deletion through ဆက်တင်များ > Data & ကိုယ်ရေးအချက်အလက် > ဖျက် Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain data is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific data processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any အချိန် without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app ပံ့ပိုးမှု feature.",
  "privacySectionContactUs": "5. Contact Us",
  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns အကြောင်း this ကိုယ်ရေးအချက်အလက် Policy or our data practices, please contact us: • Eအီးမေးလ် privacy@vitalseker.com • Sပံ့ပိုးမှု support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to အားလုံး privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
